questions: What makes an interactive website different from a static website?
first_option: Interactive websites are built for two-way communication between the user and the website and allows the user to modify the data within the server
second_option: Interactive websites have many photos and videos on the webpage.
third_option: Interactive websites are the same as static websites.
fourth_option: Interactive websites allow the user to  see the back-end of the website.
